Naturi Cora Maria Naughton -LRB- born May 20 , 1984 -RRB- is an American actress and singer-songwriter .
Naughton was one-third of the R&B trio 3LW and is known for her acting roles in Fame , Notorious , where she played Lil ' Kim , and The Playboy Club .
Naughton was a series regular in season one of the Lifetime television drama series The Client List as Kendra .
Naughton stars in the Starz drama Power as Tasha St. Patrick .